<h3><i>Conditionally adds a list of micro-behaviours.</i></h3>
<p><font size="2" color="gray">Begin micro-behaviour</font>
</p>
<p><b>DO-IF-ELSE</b></p>
<font size="2" color="gray">Begin NetLogo code:</font>
<pre>substitute-text-area-for columns: 68 rows: 5 condition true                                                
substitute-text-area-for columns: 80 rows: 5 comment ; Notes                                                                                      
do-if-else (condition)
  [add-behaviours 
       list-of-micro-behaviours "Behaviours to add if true" []]
  [add-behaviours 
       list-of-micro-behaviours "Behaviours to add if false" []]
comment</pre>
<font size="2" color="gray">End NetLogo code</font>
<h2>Related Micro-behaviours</h2>
<p><a href="DO-IF-ELSE.html">DO-IF-ELSE</a> differs from <a href="DO-IF.html">
DO-IF</a> in that it has actions 
to perform when condition is false. <a href="WHEN.html">WHEN</a> runs only once 
when the <i>condition</i> is true while <a href="WHENEVER.html">
WHENEVER</a> runs every time the <i>condition</i> is true.
<a href="DO-IF-ELSE.html">DO-IF-ELSE</a> runs if the <i>condition</i> is true now.</p>
